**Summary:**
This documentation covers the Android-Kotlin SDK for Amplitude analytics, including installation via Gradle/Maven (com.amplitude:analytics-android), configuration options like flushIntervalMillis/flushQueueSize, autocapture features for sessions/app lifecycles/screen views/deep links/element interactions, tracking methods (track/identify/revenue), user/group management, plugins system, and advanced features like COPPA control, advertising ID/app set ID usage, location tracking, and offline mode with ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE permission.

